HEADWORD: Flooring
<hw>Floor"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A platform; the bottom of a room;
a floor; pavement. See <er>Floor</er>, <pos>n.</pos></def>
<rj><au>Addison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Material for the construction of a floor or
floors.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Floorless</ent>⟦br⟧
